  "text": "Several applications of conductive polymers rely on the surface adsorption of the drug or dopant and the subsequent release from the surface. However, dexamethasone was incorporated into the PPy walls of the nanotubes. The surface and lumina of the nanotubes can, therefore, contribute to control the release of the drug [CITATION_1] .",
